# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST (Firebase Hosting)
# =============================================================================
#
# Before deploying to production:
#
# âœ… All VITE_FIREBASE_* values configured with production Firebase project
# âœ… VITE_BACKEND_API_URL points to production backend (https)
# âœ… VITE_SENTRY_DSN configured (recommended)
# âœ… VITE_SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT=production
# âœ… Build the site: npm run build
# âœ… Test locally: firebase emulators:start --only hosting
# âœ… Deploy: firebase deploy --only hosting
#
# Security reminders:
# - VITE_ variables are PUBLIC (embedded in client JavaScript)
# - Never put secrets/API keys in VITE_ variables
# - Firebase Web API key is safe to expose (protected by Firebase rules)
# - Backend should validate all requests with Firebase tokens
# - Enable Firebase App Check for additional security
#
# Performance tips:
# - Use CDN for static assets (Firebase Hosting does this)
# - Enable HTTPS (Firebase Hosting does this)
# - Monitor bundle size: npm run build -- --report
# - Use Sentry Performance Monitoring to track real user metrics
#
